REM Example 3: Graphics - Drawing a circle
10 GRAPHICS
20 COLOR 1
30 CLS
40 PRINT "Drawing a circle..."
50 FOR I = 0 TO 360 STEP 5
60 LET X = 400 + 100 * COS(I * 3.14159 / 180)
70 LET Y = 300 + 100 * SIN(I * 3.14159 / 180)
80 PLOT X, Y
90 NEXT I
100 COLOR 2
110 CIRCLE 400, 300, 150
120 COLOR 3
130 LINE 300, 300 TO 500, 300
140 LINE 400, 200 TO 400, 400
150 END
